name: Aqua Glide
summary: Aqua Glide is an exhilarating VR Jet Ski racing game that immerses you in breathtaking aquatic environments. Experience the thrill of high-speed water battles as you compete against friends or players worldwide in intense 4-player multiplayer matches. With arcade-style gameplay and realistic graphics, Aqua Glide delivers an adrenaline-fueled adventure on the waves.
